get_category_system:
می‌خواهم کالای زیر را از در یکی از این دسته بندی ها قرار دهم. با توجه به این لیست دسته بندی ها
{categories}
کدام را انتخاب می‌کنید؟ جواب را در قالب یک json بده. نمونه زیر را ببینید.
{{
  "category": "category"
}}

get_category_brand_system:
یکی از برند های لیست زیر را به پروداکت ارائه شده تخصیص بده و عنوان فارسی برند را برگردان. با توجه به این لیست برند ها {brands} کدام برند مرتبط با اطلاعات این کالاست. جواب را در قالب یک json بده. نمونه زیر را ببینید.
{{
  "brand": "brand"
}}

attribute_match_select_system:
The JSON below contains details about a product. "field name" is the name of a product attribute, "field values" contains all values that the field can have and "hint" is a hint about the field. The field type is multiple choice. I want you to extract the value or values of the field based on its name, its valid values, hint and the JSON.
If you could not find the explicit value of the field in the source JSON, match with the closest values in the field values. You should always assign a value to the field in the output. 
Return the output in JSON format. nothing more or less.

example output:
{{
    "name":"رنگ",
    "value": ["قرمز", "سبز"]
}}

attribute_match_select_user:
json:
{product}

field name: {field_name}
field values: {field_values}
hint: {hint}

attribute_match_text_system:
The JSON below contains details about a product. "field" is the name of a product attribute and "hint" is a hint about it. I want you to extract the value of the field based on its name, hint and the JSON. If you could not find the explicit value of the field, give your best guess for it. You should always assign a value to field in the output. 
Return the output in JSON format. nothing more or less.

example output:
{{
    "name":"جنس",
    "value": "پلاستیکی"
}}

attribute_match_checkbox_system:
The JSON below contains details about a product. "field name" is the name of a product attribute, "field values" contains all values that the field can have and "hint" is a hint about the field. The field type is always single choice. I want you to extract the value of the field based on its name, its valid values, hint and the JSON.
If you could not find the explicit value of the field in the source JSON, match with the closest values in the field values.You should always assign a value to the field in the output. 
Return the output in JSON format. nothing more or less.

example output:
{{
    "name":"جنس",
    "value": "پلاستیکی"
}}

